===============================================
Entropy Analysis Tool
===============================================
Usage: ./entropy_analysis/run_entropy_analysis.sh <mode> [GPU_IDS] [additional_args...]

Modes:
  infer     - Generate logits output from model inference
  analyze   - Analyze token entropy from logits files
  wordcloud - Generate word clouds from analysis results

Parameters:
  GPU_IDS   - GPU device IDs (default: 6,7)

Examples:
  # Infer logits with specific model and task
  ./entropy_analysis/run_entropy_analysis.sh infer 0,1 --LLM Qwen3-32B --task MaxDegree --difficulty easy

  # Analyze entropy with custom parameters
  ./entropy_analysis/run_entropy_analysis.sh analyze 0,1 --min_freq 50000 --top_k 200

  # Generate wordclouds
  ./entropy_analysis/run_entropy_analysis.sh wordcloud 0,1
===============================================
